reviewText: Sid and Marty Krofft Collector's Edition Volume 7. Episodes on this volume include HR Pufnstuf: Birthday Party, Bugaloos: Courage Come Home, Dr Shrinker: Shake Up, Sigmund and the Sea Monsters: Monster Rock Festival, Far Out Space Nuts: Fantastic Journey, and another episode of Dr Shrinker: Shrinkie Sale. This volume was part of the Columbia House series of 10 volumes.
